The paper deals with social networks and information propagation, which are topics that fall under the categories of social networks (cs.SOC), information retrieval (cs.IR), and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also discusses the problem of filter bubbles, which is a concern in the field of cybersecurity (cs.CYBER).
